reviewText: This hentai was really good, it was kinda sad because her husband died 3 years ago. Without her husband the only thing she could do, is pleasure herself alone. Another thing is this dvd is getting hard to find, eBay has a couple going for $ 112.00 a piece. Amazon has one for 24.98 used very good, and another for over $ 100.00 new. I was lucky to find one for $ 24.99 new. Anyway it is a pretty nice hentai.
